"title": "5782: agony",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5782: agony",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Intense suffering of body, mind or spirit, brought about by illness, death or the judgment of God.</p>\n<h2>Examples of agony</h2>\n<h3>Agony of body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:2\">PSA 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:10\">PSA 31:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:3\">ISA 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:21\">JHN 16:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:5\">REV 9:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:10\">REV 16:10</a></p>\n<h3>Agony of heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19\">JER 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:25\">DEU 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:16\">1SA 1:16</a> <em>Hannah prays for a son</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:2\">JOB 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:11\">JOB 7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:3\">PSA 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:17\">PSA 25:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:7\">PSA 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:8\">PSA 38:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4\">PSA 55:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:14\">ISA 65:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:33\">MRK 14:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:44\">LUK 22:44</a> <em>Jesus Christ prays on the Mount of Olives</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:2\">ROM 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of agony</h2>\n<h3>Illness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:18\">JER 15:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:16-Job30:17\">JOB 30:16–30:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:2-Ps6:3\">PSA 6:2–6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:7\">PSA 38:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:29\">PSA 69:29</a></p>\n<h3>Death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:5\">JOB 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:4-Ps18:6\">PSA 18:4–18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4\">PSA 55:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a></p>\n<h3>The judgment of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:24-Luke16:25\">LUK 16:24–16:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:19\">JER 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:16\">EZK 30:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:10\">MIC 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:5\">ZEC 9:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:13\">MAT 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:51\">MAT 24:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:30\">MAT 25:30</a></p>",
